		<!-- message -->
		<div>well really i think it depends on your group configuration, and how well the people know their classes. Normally i would stay on the mob that i had cast CD on, and let the cleric and chanter worry about the adds.  A good chanter shouldnt have much problem dealing with 2 mobs.<br />
However, assuming you are killing mobs above level 55, you could use fear to try and pull them off the chanter. this is fa irly decent aggro and wont damage or dot the mobs. if your fighting mobs below level 55 you could try the terror line, but i havent had much luck with those.</div>
